The,Audiences,API,by,MasterCard,identifies,user,segments,with,a,higher,probability,to,make,continuous,purchases,within,a,category,This,API,provides,purchasing,insight,and,forms,audience,profiles,based,on,annually,aggregated,transactions,Audiences,are,represented,by,behaviors,such,as,number,of,transactions,frequency,of,purchase,location,and,merchant,category,The,Audiences,API,follows,the,REST,architectural,style,XML,is,used,for,data,exchange,and,OAuth,for,authentication